commit.title: Fix backtraces in conversion anomalies caught by Reductionops.
commit.message:
Fix backtraces in conversion anomalies caught by Reductionops.

The call to is_anomaly actually destroyed the backtrace, because it would
call arbitrary code, in particular in Himsg which relied internally on
raising exceptions.
